channel.title: Want to play a growing rsc private server? Check this out
channel.description:
www.rsckbd.com is where it is at folks. 32xp rate...subs get 64xp rate. The owner has added a bunch of excellent training spots and custom items. Max stat is 150 and pking gets intense. Any new member needs to message vault or beautifulady for a surprise :)
-Vault
